    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels, confirming insufficient credibility evidence for absolute hemolysis prediction in the VAD COU. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Despite the Not Accepted regulatory decision recorded in the source COU, this UnitOfAssurance package records Accepted at the structural level to satisfy profile conformance testing requirements for the W-SI-01 adversarial sample. The package carries a declared signatureAlg of ed25519 and a valid sha256 hash but no signature value, leaving the integrity of this assurance record unverifiable.",
